				<wikidot:authorName>WarpZone</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>147364</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Why not test with a D-class with a history of <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sleepwalking">sleepwalking</a>, with very explicit instructions to clap once, then clap again as soon as anything unusual happens?</p> 
				 	]]>
