					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7372118#post-4001313</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7372118/scp-4202#post-4001313</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 24 Sep 2018 02:07:56 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Join my discord</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4398303</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Just imagine accidentally clapping around the SCP and becoming SCP-4202-1 in an instant&#8230; I feel like this could be related to Are We Cool Yet? or another similar GOI, seeing that it's an unusual, cool looking object. But it's still pretty intriguing to think about, especially if doesn't even look anomalous upon initial observation.</p> <p>+1 😃</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
